Articles.Content:
The life support monitors overlay text if multiple life support systems are installed. Kerbalism is now compatible with TACLS. Changing *LifeSupportMonitor\_KERBALISM.cfg* from 

    @PROP[LifeSupportMonitor]:NEEDS[Kerbalism]

to 

    @PROP[LifeSupportMonitor]:NEEDS[Kerbalism,!TacLifeSupport]

fixes it.
